txt.en: The Corsairs in Lamedon appear to have been busy looting and stealing from the townsfolk of this peaceful part of western Gondor.\n\nYou should recover stolen coin-purses from the Corsairs in their northern encampment.
Recover stolen coin-purses from corsair toughs
You have recovered a number of stolen coin-purses from the Corsairs who have set up their camp in the swamps of northern Lamedon.
